      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V modeled as bilinear isotropic hardening elastoplastic continuum. This model form is well-established for quasi-static spinal implant loading. Frictional contact (mu=0.3) at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces. Augmented Lagrange contact formulation validated against Hertzian benchmark. Model form uncertainty assessed as low for the QoIs of interest."
